* If $$Y_1,Y_2$$ are subsets of some set $$W$$ and $$X = Y_1 \cap Y_2,$$ then $$P = Y_1 \cup Y_2.$$

* The pushout of groups is the [[amalgamated free product|Amalgamated free product]] $$Y_1 \star_X Y_2.$$